I"{<p>source: <a href="https://solidfoundationwebdev.com/blog/posts/how-to-easily-convert-mkv-to-mp4-from-the-terminal">How To Easily Convert MKV To MP4 From The Terminal - Solid Foundation Web Development</a></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>$ ffmpeg -i my_movie.mkv -vcodec copy -acodec copy my_movie.mp4</p>
</blockquote>

